m/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"4032\" height=\"2268\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 6 set against some flowers\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/06/img_0519.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe know that the trifold phone is something the brand has been working on, and while the details have been scarce, we could end up getting our first look at the handset during its upcoming Unpacked event. However, this doesn\u0026#39;t come to us through official channels, but instead, through a \u003ca href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/5181901551700514\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003epost on Weibo\u003c/a\u003e (via \u003ca href=\"https://9to5google.com/2025/06/27/rumor-samsung-tri-fold-unveiled-alongside-galaxy-z-fold-7-with-october-launch/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e9to5Google\u003c/a\u003e). \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eAs far as other details, according to the leaker, Samsung will announce its upcoming trifold phone at the upcoming Galaxy Unpacked event in July, but it won\u0026#39;t actually be available that same day. Instead, it will have a delayed release, with the information stating that it could be made official sometime in October. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eFor the most part, this could be an interesting strategy, considering that most people could be more interested in the trifold than the new Galaxy Z Fold 7. While we have seen \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/huawei-mate-xt-design-makes-sense-for-foldable/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea trifold phone launch\u003c/a\u003e, it has \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/huawei-mate-xt-trifold-phone-global-launch/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003enot been made available inside the US\u003c/a\u003e, which would make Samsung the sole company to make a trifold available in markets outside of Asia. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eWith that said, this trifold phone could be quite expensive, as the technology is still in its infancy. While it\u0026#39;s hard to speculate on just how much it will cost, but we have to imagine that it will cost more than the current foldables out, which could have the price balloon over $2,000. In addition to that, we\u0026#39;ve also heard rumors that Samsung is \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-hints-at-galaxy-z-fold-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eworking on foldable phone that\u0026#39;s an Ultra variant\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eRegardless of what gets announced, the event will be quite stacked when it comes to product announcements, with rumors indicating that the Z Fold 7 and Z Flip 7 will make an appearance, along with new Galaxy Watch 8 wearables. For the most part, this could be the most exciting Samsung event in years. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eAnd just in case you\u0026#39;re interested, you can currently \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-50-credit-galaxy-unpacked-2025/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003escore a free $50 credit\u003c/a\u003e ahead of the Galaxy Unpacked event by \u003ca href=\"https://shop-links.co/link/?exclusive=1\u0026amp;publisher_slug=androidpolice\u0026amp;article_name=Samsung+could+pull+a+Galaxy+25+Edge+with+its+upcoming+trifold+phone\u0026amp;article_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidpolice.com%2Fsamsung-galaxy-trifold-phone-at-galaxy-unpacked%2F\u0026amp;u1=UUapUeUpU1028727\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fsmartphones%2Fthe-next-galaxy%2Freserve%2F\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow sponsored\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eregistering to purchase whatever foldables are announced\u003c/a\u003e. The good news is there\u0026#39;s no commitment to buy, so if you don\u0026#39;t really see anything interesting, you can just ignore the credit. So if you\u0026#39;re even the least bit interested in what\u0026#39;s to come, we recommend registering. \u003c/p\u003e        \n    \n                \n                                \n    \n                            \n    \n        \n        \n    \n\n        \n\n    \n\n        \n                    \n    \n                                                            \n    \u003cdiv data-show-streamrentbuy-links=\"false\" data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"6acd-44c2-9891ff33e9fe\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/samsung-logo.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\" data-stnl-group-once=\"3LWqshGo2k\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/samsung-logo.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=420\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/samsung-logo.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=420\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                        